.TH "LIGHTNING-NODE-INVOICE-STATS" 1 "May 2026" "lightning 0.6.0" "User Commands"
.SH NAME
lightning-node-invoice-stats \- show invoice count and revenue summary
.SH SYNOPSIS
.B lightning node-invoice-stats
.SH DESCRIPTION
Returns a summary of invoices grouped by status and total received amount.
.PP
Output:
.nf
{"total":N, "paid":N, "unpaid":N, "expired":N, "total_received_msat":N}
.fi
.SH EXIT STATUS
.TP
.B 0
Always.
.SH SEE ALSO
.BR lightning-invoice-summary (1),
.BR lightning-invoice-list-paid (1)
